#<AdxTL>@(#)0.0.0.0 $Revision$ 

Local Char PLANTA(GLONFCY)
Local Char ARTICULO(GLONITM)
Local Char FECHA(8)
Local Date IPTDAT
Local Char PMP(20)
adxifs = ";"
adxirs = chr$(13)+chr$(10)

Openi filpath("BQT","UPDPMP","TXT") Using [PMP]

Rdseq PLANTA,ARTICULO,FECHA,PMP Using [PMP]
While fstat=0
  IPTDAT = gdat$(val(mid$(FECHA,7,2)),val(mid$(FECHA,5,2)),val(mid$(FECHA,1,4)))
  Call UPDPMP(PLANTA,ARTICULO,IPTDAT,val(PMP))
  Rdseq PLANTA,ARTICULO,FECHA,PMP Using [PMP]
Wend


End

Subprog UPDPMP(PLANTA,ARTICULO,FECHA,COSTE)
Value Char PLANTA()
Value Char ARTICULO()
Value Date FECHA
Value Decimal COSTE

Local Mask CHGVAL

Gosub OUVRE_BOITE From SUBCGV
Gosub DEBUT From SUBCGV



[M:CGV]STOFCY=PLANTA: Call AM_STOFCY([M:CGV]STOFCY) From SUBCGV
[M:CGV]ITMREF=ARTICULO:
Call AM_ITMREF([M:CGV]ITMREF) From SUBCGV
Call C_ITMREF([M:CGV]ITMREF) From SUBCGV
If [M:CGV]AVCBASQTP=0: End: Endif
[M:CGV]IPTDAT=FECHA
[M:CGV]AVCBASAMT=COSTE*[M:CGV]AVCBASQTP: Call AM_AVCBASAMT([M:CGV]AVCBASAMT) From SUBCGV

Gosub OK From SUBCGV

End

